# The record repository is the pristine proof-of-work database. It tracks only
# record content and the governed root files. Nothing else belongs here.
#
# The validate workflow installs js-yaml ephemerally in the CI runner with
# "npm init -y" and "npm install --no-save"; those artifacts must never be
# committed, and neither must local environment or OS files.

node_modules/
package.json
package-lock.json
.env
.env.*
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
